ZH: 我姐姐是个家政管理员。
EN: My sister is a household manager.

ZH: 家政服务包括打扫卫生和做饭。
EN: Household services include cleaning and cooking.

ZH: 我们每个月请家政帮我们打扫房间。
EN: We hire a housekeeper to clean our rooms every month.

ZH: 家政公司提供家庭清洁服务。
EN: The household company provides home cleaning services.

ZH: 家政工人每天都会来到我们家里。
EN: The household worker comes to our house every day.

ZH: 我的邻居是一名家政服务员。
EN: My neighbor is a household service worker.

ZH: 在这家宾馆，家政服务是包含在费用里的。
EN: In this hotel, housekeeping service is included in the cost.

ZH: 家政工作不仅是为了生计，也是一种责任和乐趣。
EN: Household work is not only for a living, but also a responsibility and joy.

ZH: 我喜欢在家做家政工作。
EN: I enjoy doing household chores at home.

ZH: 家政工作需要细心和耐心。
EN: Household work requires attention to detail and patience.

ZH: 她的工作主要是在家政公司结算薪水。
EN: Her job mainly involves settling salaries in the household company.

ZH: 家政部门提供了培训和教育课程。
EN: The household department provides training and educational courses.

ZH: 家政服务员负责整理客人的房间。
EN: The household service worker is responsible for tidying up the guest rooms.

ZH: 她的业务范围包括家政服务和育婴。
EN: Her business scope includes household services and child care.

ZH: 家政管理人员需要良好的组织能力。
EN: Household managers need good organizational skills.

ZH: 家政工作者需要具备一定的经验和技能。
EN: Household workers need to have certain experience and skills.

ZH: 你能介绍一些家政公司给我吗？
EN: Can you introduce me to some household companies?

ZH: 家政工作要求每天准时出勤。
EN: Household work requires punctual attendance every day.

ZH: 家政服务是社会底层的重要部分。
EN: Household services are an important part of the lower social strata.

ZH: 家政技能也可以成为一个有价值的职业。
EN: Household skills can also be a valuable profession.
